{"tid":2047811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小泉今日子抵制港版国安法「已經簽名連署」","createTime":"2020-06-02T11:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T15:06:38.000Z","uid":184679,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"25b36b179b6e62a86a7d4444fd0ad2272c89c335","tid":2047811,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T11:04:05.000Z","msg":"中國大陸強推「港版國安法」招來國際社會批評、抵制，54歲日本資深女星小泉今日子，日前在個人推特表態反對此惡法，還霸氣表示「已經簽名了」，令香港網友感動不已。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/MFYLTJe4sWPYgP2Hm.F6gw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/hTPLMxAT.OTTkJt3FIF_sg--~B/aD00NTA7dz04MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/entertainment.nownews.hk/425373c4b835eac946a818f46c0dde62\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FMFYLTJe4sWPYgP2Hm.F6gw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FhTPLMxAT.OTTkJt3FIF_sg--~B%2FaD00NTA7dz04MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fentertainment.nownews.hk%2F425373c4b835eac946a818f46c0dde62&h=57849d3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／jvcmusic官方網站、小泉今日子推特）<br />\n<br />\n國際特赦組織日本分會（Amnesty International Japan）發起「阻止香港國家安全法立法」連署活動，小泉今日子上月31日在她的官方推特上轉PO連署文章及連結，指自己已經簽名響應，而該連署目標人數為7000人，目前有3691人參加。<br />\n<br />\n小泉今日子出道38年，影視歌三棲的她為80年代當紅女歌手，人氣之高與松田聖子、中森明菜被日媒封為三大超人氣女偶像，戲劇代表作有電視劇《戀愛總動員》、《小海女》、電影《大搜查線》、《陰陽師》等，她的前夫為知名演員永瀨正敏。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/重量級日星發聲-她抵制港版國安法-已經簽名連署-101428651.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F%E7%B4%9A%E6%97%A5%E6%98%9F%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2-%E5%A5%B9%E6%8A%B5%E5%88%B6%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E5%B7%B2%E7%B6%93%E7%B0%BD%E5%90%8D%E9%80%A3%E7%BD%B2-101428651.html&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=3790a3f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/重量級日星發聲-她抵制港版國安法-已經簽名連署-101428651.html</a>"},{"pid":"956e0fe539945d76b90577f7dfbd349eecc6c963","tid":2047811,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T11:04:30.000Z","msg":"街頭抗爭已經冇必要<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2047807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2047807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"241a01ec8246b27e32df77759d389fe035bf58a0","tid":2047811,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T11:12:56.000Z","msg":"睇下係日本個陳美齡有冇出過聲？<br />\n成日就想返黎香港搵高官做<br />\n（依家聽講人在香港）"},{"pid":"0e2db4afc0d47ffd3286e25622a8a082bdd746a6","tid":2047811,"uid":161430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T11:23:56.000Z","msg":"80年代好似係日本三大歌歌姬<br />\n佢同中森明菜<br />\n<img src=\"https://auctions.c.yimg.jp/images.auctions.yahoo.co.jp/image/dr000/auc0511/users/21d1b756ed983566a26ae8be99c7c40a1701cd96/i-img480x640-1573106273jg7zlg576258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fauctions.c.yimg.jp%2Fimages.auctions.yahoo.co.jp%2Fimage%2Fdr000%2Fauc0511%2Fusers%2F21d1b756ed983566a26ae8be99c7c40a1701cd96%2Fi-img480x640-1573106273jg7zlg576258.jpg&h=974aa3a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinacn20100/205/w640h365/20191009/ef03-ifrwayw9054473.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fsinacn20100%2F205%2Fw640h365%2F20191009%2Fef03-ifrwayw9054473.jpg&h=38837110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://twgreatdaily.com/images/elastic/y2N/y2NE-mwBJleJMoPMFb7E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwgreatdaily.com%2Fimages%2Felastic%2Fy2N%2Fy2NE-mwBJleJMoPMFb7E.jpg&h=5cefadc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9803a856ad9e001f01f62a001db61cf452191bf6","tid":2047811,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e2db4afc0d47ffd3286e25622a8a082bdd746a6","tid":2047811,"uid":161430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T11:23:56.000Z","msg":"80年代好似係日本三大歌歌姬<br />